rComments: The worst prof you can take a class with. Is rude to her students, Doesnt provide clear instructions for assignments, Avoid taking classes with her unless youre prepared for unnecessary stress and belittling based on your major.

Weekly mini-quizes on readings that actually force you to keep up and to engage in the class discussion. Briefs you on how Anthropology works before she gets into core material. Very cute with her messy bun and her quasi-anxious demeanour. Small class with lots of interesting topics that are very neatly covered. Highly recommend.

Lots of open class discussion. Classes could be a bit disorganized but she was clearly passionate about her subject material. Also, she gave us PDFs to read so that we didn't have to buy a textbook. She will give little tests on the readings so make sure you do them.
teacherRatingTags: ['Beware of pop quizzes', 'Get ready to read']
